[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]颁奖的[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（又称[[奥斯卡金像奖|学院奖]]）中有4个演员类的奖项，分别是[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角]]、[[奥斯卡最佳女主角奖|女主角]]、[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|男配角]]和[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|女配角奖]]。历史上曾有过多位演员在一部电影中完全没有说过[[英语|英语]]而获得提名，其中1961年首次有这样的演员胜出。不过根据学院的规则，演员要因这样的一次电影演出而获提名，该片必须则在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的[[洛杉矶县|洛杉矶县]]进行过商业发行，并且其对白需要附有英文字幕。<ref name="Rules">{{cite web|title=Special Rules for the Best Foreign Language Film Award|url=http://www.oscars.org/79academyawards/rules/rule14.html|accessdate=2008-07-25|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080917073025/http://www.oscars.org/79academyawards/rules/rule14.html|archivedate=2008-09-17|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

{{As of|2022}}，一共有49位演员因在电影中没有说英语而获得奥斯卡金像奖表演类提名，其中有12位最终获奖。7位获得过多项提名，分别是：[[馬切洛·馬斯楚安尼|馬切洛·馬斯楚安尼]]三次获男主角奖提名<ref name="MoviefoneMastroianniAwards">{{cite web|title=Marcello Mastroianni - Awards|url=http://www.moviefone.com/celebrity/marcello-mastroianni/1351050/awards|accessdate=2013-10-16|publisher=Moviefone|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223115304/http://www.moviefone.com/celebrity/marcello-mastroianni/1351050/awards|archivedate=2012-02-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>，[[伊莎贝尔·阿佳妮|伊莎贝尔·阿佳妮]]两次获女主角奖提名<ref name="MoviefoneAdjaniAwards">{{cite web|title=Isabelle Adjani - Awards|url=http://www.moviefone.com/celebrity/isabelle-adjani/1199276/awards|accessdate=2013-10-16|publisher=Moviefone|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223115330/http://www.moviefone.com/celebrity/isabelle-adjani/1199276/awards|archivedate=2012-02-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>，[[索非娅·罗兰|索非娅·罗兰]]两次获女主角奖提名，其中一次获奖<ref name="MoviefoneLorenAwards">{{cite web|title=Sophia Loren - Awards|url=http://www.moviefone.com/celebrity/sophia-loren/1080617/awards|accessdate=2013-10-16|publisher=Moviefone|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223115401/http://www.moviefone.com/celebrity/sophia-loren/1080617/awards|archivedate=2012-02-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>，[[麗芙·烏曼|麗芙·烏曼]]两次获女主角奖提名<ref name="NYTimesLivUllmann">{{cite web|title=Liv Ullmann - Awards|url=http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/114863/Liv-Ullmann/awards|accessdate=2013-10-16|work=The New York Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004172246/http://movies.nytimes.com/person/114863/Liv-Ullmann/awards|archivedate=2012-10-04|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="LATVolver">{{cite web|title=Toronto fest-goers love Almodóvar's latest|url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2006/09/festgoers_lover.html|accessdate=2013-10-16|author=O'Neil, Tom|date=2006-09-08|work=Los Angeles Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214171215/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2006/09/festgoers_lover.html|archivedate=2012-02-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>，[